==English==
===Noun===
'''pie-eater'''

#(''pejorative'') a person from [[Wigan]] in northern [[England]] or the surrounding area
#:'''2005''' &mdash; Wiganers do like pies, but the term '''Pie-eaters''' is actually an insult, dating back to a pit strike when Wigan miners were starved back to work before their St Helens counterparts, thereby eating humble pie. &mdash; - ''The Observer'', "Get past the pies and there's a football team", 7 Aug 2005